::Feline::

She smiled at him.  She walked up to him and put her hands on his 
shoulders. She brought her tail up and wrapped it anound the back 
side of his neck.
"Ok handsome, I need you to do something for me. I need you to hit me 
a few times. OK?" she smiled and kissed him on the cheek. "Please? It 
will help create the illusion of me escaping from the naughty, evil 
Allience."
